<title>USA: Hyperion Software CFO Ricciardi to retire.</title>
<headline>Hyperion Software CFO Ricciardi to retire.</headline>
<dateline>STAMFORD, Conn. 1996-12-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Hyperion Software Corp said on Tuesday that Lucy Rae Ricciardi, senior vice president and chief financial officer, will retire effective July 31, 1997.</p>
<p>Following her retirement, Ricciardi will serve as senior advisor to Hyperion, the company said.</p>
<p>It said Ricciardi will play a key role in searching for her successor and ensuring a smooth transition.</p>
</text>
